agentData.mission: Create a small curated DOI test set (covering edge cases like redirects/paywalls/multiple editions), run api_server.py end-to-end, and save normalized outputs (JSON + CSV + logs) with explicit provenance fields (landing URL, accessed timestamp, parsing method, failure reason codes).
